name: Deep Sea Diver Pendant Necklace
description:
Come explore the deep blue sea.

This nautical inspired pendant features a found illustration of an antique diving suit. The illustration was restored, printed on a cream colored archival card stock and then encased with jewelry grade resin in a brass bezel. The result is beautiful pendant with a glassy, domed surface.

The pendant measures 1"(2.5cm) and 3/4"(1.9cm) by 1/8"(.3cm) and is attached to a brass bail. This listing comes with a 19" bronze chain and matching clasps.

---

All items come wrapped and carefully packed in bubble wrap for shipping. Orders are sent USPS First Class mail, but other shipping options (including international) are available.

name: Vintage Map Stud Earrings - Blue
description:
Perfect for geography lovers and travelers alike.

These mini blue vintage map earrings are back and have been upgraded from 6mm to 8mm (see fourth image for details). This new slightly larger style is still as lovely as ever but offers more clarity and depth than the previous version. Created by encasing blue toned vintage map print with resin in a bronze plated brass bezel. They are lightweight and comfortable to wear.

The earrings are approximately 8mm in diameter and the post is 12mm(.5") long. The studs are bronze plated brass and come with matching backs.

Note: While the earrings are water-resistant, I would not suggest showering/swimming with these on as it can affect the resin over time.

name: Icarus - Steampunk Bronze Feather Necklace with Inset Gears
description:
Steampunk bronze feather necklace with gears inspired by Greek mythology.

This unique necklace features a bronze feather with a 6mm brass bezel with inset gears. The found gear pieces are set on printed card stock inside a brass bezel and sealed with a domed layer of resin for a glossy finish.

The pendant measures approximately 1.63"(4.3cm) long by 5/8"(1.7cm) wide. It is attached to a 19" bronze plated brass chain with matching clasp. The finished piece hangs at a slight angle.

---

All items come wrapped suitably for gift giving and are carefully packed in bubble wrap for shipping. Orders are sent USPS First Class mail, but other shipping options (including international) are available.

name: Hardware Earrings - Copper Hex Nuts (large)
description:
Show your love for hardware with these unique earrings.

These industrial inspired earrings were created by casting resin replicas of hex nuts. They were then hand painted to look like aged copper and finished with an extra layer of resin for shine and protection. The result is lightweight, comfortable and a great gift for anyone.

The earrings measure approximately 1/2"(1.3cm) in diameter and are securely attached to surgical steel posts.

Note: each set of earrings are hand painted and may vary slightly from the ones pictured.
---

All items come wrapped and carefully packed in bubble wrap for shipping. Orders are sent USPS First Class mail, but other shipping options (including international) are available. Just convo me!
